&lt;li&gt;Explore and propose new ways to express AKQA’s brand, not solely maintain consistency with existing guidelines&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Responsible for asset management, collation, and archiving&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Consistently deliver high quality work on time, supporting the wider team to deliver high quality work within required timeframes&lt;/li&gt;
