&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficient in the formal elements of design, including typography, layout, balance, hierarchy, proportion, rhythm, emphasis, and unity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficient and confident in working in Figma. This includes having an understanding of website design and how a design system works.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficient and confident in working with Creative Cloud applications. More specifically be confident in using the design applications such as Photoshop, Illustrator, InDesign. Having an understanding of post production for photography using Lightroom. Plus having a basic understanding of animation/editing in programs such as After Effects and/or Premiere Pro. This also includes intelligently organising files for design iteration and web production.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create original designs that align to project goals, creative direction, fluid templates, and standards&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bring fresh thinking to how the brand is expressed across formats, balancing originality with AKQA’s creative standards&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Consult with technical disciplines to ensure designs work within given limitations, and files are prepared with all necessary information to support the design intent&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be accountable for the quality of all design deliverables, reviewing final work with high attention to detail to ensure layout, images, and typography meet AKQA standards for creative excellence&lt;/li&gt;
