&lt;li&gt;Ability to balance stakeholder expectations with project realities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong sense of personal responsibility for their work and their teammates&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Diligent, flexible, resourceful, and independent, with a strong work ethic, a can-do attitude, and enthusiasm for learning new things.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
