&lt;p&gt;At AKQA (part of WPP), we believe in the imaginative application of art and science to create beautiful ideas, products and services. With an entrepreneurial and collaborative approach, we design adaptive digital products, services and experiences that capture the imagination and deliver meaningful returns for our clients.&amp;nbsp; At AKQA, you will help define the next era of AI-native customer experiences,&amp;nbsp; not as a future concept, but as live products and platforms already moving into the world.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The industry is entering a structural shift. Traditional digital experiences are becoming AI-native experiences, interfaces assembled in real-time around intent, conversation, retrieval and contextual generation. At AKQA, we are not exploring this future theoretically. We are already building it.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a Director, Generative AI Experience Engineering to help define and deliver the next generation of AI-native customer experiences across commerce, content and customer interfaces for some of the world’s most ambitious brands.&lt;/p&gt;
