&lt;li&gt;Design systems that support conversational rendering, dynamic content assembly, streaming UX and adaptive interfaces.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Actively experiment with AI tooling, workflows and engineering methodologies, bringing forward-thinking ideas into production environments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
