&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;At AKQA (part of WPP), we believe in the imaginative application of art and science to create ideas, products, and services that move the world forward. We exist at the intersection of design, technology, and culture — creating work that is as meaningful as it is beautiful.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
